{"tid":1265202,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"方舟計劃支持者同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-29T05:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T08:34:18.000Z","uid":105042,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5572b6b5897625d3c5137f75ff5ef54a4ce74f","tid":1265202,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:35:08.000Z","msg":"大家係咁講租邊到/買邊到，不如講下目標要幾大塊地先？<br />\n<br />\n香港面積大約得1100平方公里，就住咗接近800萬人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我當有200萬人想參加方舟計劃，其實500平方公里嘅地已經絕對夠用。而單計一個高雄市面積已經有接近3000平方公里。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果我地定咗目標，再對外宣傳我地只想有一個容身之地，咁樣到時我地問人租地/買地，人地就容易啲有個預算，無咁易有人反感。"},{"pid":"b9767e8bac5d8da25e6bd1891b66822a583dbf98","tid":1265202,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:40:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa3766aa388f503a195e964c78ca15671760ba5b","tid":1265202,"uid":105042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"e61bfb86c183e3ae5e3bd192ce4905434b32bbd5","tid":1265202,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9db54268b8f3bf0b6b226cc2068e03c86a015251","tid":1265202,"uid":3063,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:58:38.000Z","msg":"事實上 無可能淨係容身之所<br />\n會污染 會搶人地工作機會 福利<br />\n資源"},{"pid":"0db62b04874c6b12b124a25d580128e34d681b85","tid":1265202,"uid":105042,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"9db54268b8f3bf0b6b226cc2068e03c86a015251","tid":1265202,"uid":3063,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:58:38.000Z","msg":"事實上 無可能淨係容身之所<br />\n會污染 會搶人地工作機會 福利<br />\n資源"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"就算呢啲係事實，我地都要美化佢，爭取多啲人認同，可能係好虛偽，但為咗香港人整體利益，真係要盡